// The general event-log seam (`Stdlib.EventLog`) that sync reads from. Reading past the end of the log
// leaves the cursor unchanged ‚Äî the "already current" shape a peer serves a caught-up puller. The full
// since‚Üíappend‚Üíconverge path (origin_ts preservation + fold) is covered in the F# suite
// (OpsProjections.Tests); this pins the Dark-side read contract.

module EventLog =
  Stdlib.Tuple3.third (Stdlib.EventLog.since 999999999L) = 999999999L
